content: निवि(बि)ड {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Without space or interstices, close, compact. {@--2@} Firm, tight, fast; निबिडो मुष्टिः <ls>R. 9. 58</ls>, <ls n="R.">19. 44.</ls> {@--3@} Thick, impervious, dense, impenetrable; <ls>R. 11 15.</ls> {@--4@} Gross, coarse. {@--5@} Bulky, large. {@--6@} Crooked-nosed.
